definition.value: Catalysis of the reaction -  3,5-dichlorophenylcarboximide + OH- -eq- (3,5-dichlorophenylurea)acetate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  epsilon-caprolactam + H2O -eq- H+ + 6-aminohexanoate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  cyanuric acid + H2O -eq- biuret + CO2.
Catalysis of the reaction -  ammelide + H2O -eq- cyanuric acid + NH3.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2-chloro-4-hydroxy-6-amino-1,3,5-triazine + OH- -eq- 2,4-dihydroxy-6-amino-1,3,5-triazine + Cl-.
Catalysis of the reaction -  ammeline + H2O -eq- ammelide + NH3.
Catalysis of the reaction -  deisopropylhydroxyatrazine + H2O -eq- NH3 + 2,4-dihydroxy-6-(N'-ethyl)amino-1,3,5-triazine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2,4-dihydroxy-6-(N'-ethyl)amino-1,3,5-triazine + H2O -eq- CH3CH2NH2 + cyanuric acid.
Catalysis of the reaction -  5,10-methenyl-5,6,7,8-tetrahydromethanopterin + H(2)O -eq- N(5)-formyl-5,6,7,8-tetrahydromethanopterin + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  H(2)O + 2 H(+) + thiocyanate -eq- carbonyl sulfide + NH(4)(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  3,5-dibromo-4-hydroxybenzonitrile + 2 H(2)O -eq- 3,5-dibromo-4-hydroxybenzoate + NH(4)(+). Involved in the bacterial degradation of the herbicide bromoxynil.
Catalysis of the reaction -  R-CN + H2O -eq- R-COOH + NH3.
Catalysis of the reaction -  4-(ethylamino)-2-hydroxy-6-(isopropylamino)-1,3,5-triazine + H2O -eq- N-isopropylammelide + ethylamine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  N-isopropylammelide + H2O -eq- cyanuric acid + isopropylamine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  cis,cis-2-hydroxy-6-oxohept-2,4-dienoate + OH- -eq- cis-2-hydroxypenta-2,4-dienoate + acetate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  dihydrophloroglucinol + OH- -eq- 3-hydroxy-5-oxohexanoate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2-hydroxy-6-oxo-7-methylocta-2,4-dienoate + H2O -eq- cis-2-hydroxypenta-2,4-dienoate + isobutyrate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2-hydroxy-6-oxo-(2'-aminophenyl)-hexa-2,4-dienoate + H2O -eq- 2-aminobenzoate + cis-2-hydroxypenta-2,4-dienoate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2-hydroxy-6-oxoocta-2,4-dienoate + H2O -eq- H+ + propanoate + cis-2-hydroxypenta-2,4-dienoate.

Catalysis of the reaction -  6-oxo-2-hydroxy-7-(4'-chlorophenyl)-3,8,8-trichloroocta-2Z,4Z,7-trienoate + H2O -eq- 2-(4'-chlorophenyl)-3,3-dichloropropenoate + cis-2-Hydroxy-3-chloropenta-2,4-dienone + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (2E,4Z)-2-hydroxy-6-oxonona-2,4-dienedioate + H2O -eq- (2E)-2-hydroxypenta-2,4-dienoate + H+ + succinate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2,4,6-trioxoheptanoate + H2O -eq- acetylpyruvate + acetate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  acetylpyruvate + H(2)O -eq- acetate + H(+) + pyruvate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2,6-dioxo-6-phenylhexa-3-enoate + H2O -eq- benzoate + 2-oxopent-4-enoate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2-hydroxymuconate semialdehyde + H2O -eq- formate + 2-oxopent-4-enoate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  trans-3-chloroacrylic acid + H2O -eq- H+ + malonate semialdehyde.

Catalysis of the reaction -  alkyl halide + H2O -eq- alcohol + HCl. Substrates are 1,3(R),4,6(R)-tetrachloro-1,4-cyclohexadiene (forms 2,4,5-trichloro-2,5-cyclohexadiene-1-ol) and 2,4,5-trichloro-2,5-cyclohexadiene-1-ol (forms 2,5-dichloro-2,5-cyclohexadiene-1,4-diol).
Catalysis of the reaction -  trichloroacetate + 2 H2O -eq- 3 H+ + 3 Cl- + oxalate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  dichloroacetate + H2O -eq- 2 HCl + glyoxylate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  1-halo or 1-pseudohalo-S-triazine -eq- 1-hydroxy-S-triazine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  cis-3-chloroacrylic acid + H2O -eq- H+ + HCl + malonate semialdehyde.
Catalysis of the reaction -  deisopropyldeethylatrazine + H2O -eq- 2-chloro-4-hydroxy-6-amino-1,3,5-triazine + NH3.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (S)-2-haloacid + H2O -eq- (R)-2-hydroxyacid + halide.
Catalysis of the reaction -  haloacetate + H2O -eq- glycolate + halide.
Catalysis of the reaction -  1-haloalkane + H2O -eq- a primary alcohol + halide.
Catalysis of the reaction -  4-chlorobenzoyl-CoA + H2O -eq- 4-hydroxybenzoyl CoA + chloride.
Catalysis of the reaction -  atrazine + H(2)O -eq- 4-(ethylamino)-2-hydroxy-6-(isopropylamino)-1,3,5-triazine + chloride + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  cyclohexylsulfamate + H(2)O -eq- cyclohexylamine + sulfate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2-hydroxy-3-carboxy-6-oxo-7-methylocta-2,4-dienoate -eq- CO2 + 2-hydroxy-6-oxo-7-methylocta-2,4-dienoate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  bis(4-chlorophenyl)acetate + H+ -eq- CO2 + bis(4-chlorophenyl)methane. Bis(4-chlorophenyl)acetate is also known as DDA -  bis(4-chlorophenyl)methane is also known as DDM.
Catalysis of the reaction -  3,5-dibromo-4-hydroxybenzoate + H+ -eq- CO2 + 2,6-dibromophenol.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2-hydroxyisobutyrate + H+ -eq- CO2 + 2-propanol.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2-hydroxy-2-methyl-1,3-dicarbonate + H+ -eq- CO2 + L-lactate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  4,5-dihydroxyphthalate -eq- 3,4-dihydroxybenzoate + CO2.
Catalysis of the reaction -  gallate + H(+) -eq- CO(2) + pyrogallol.
Catalysis of the reaction -  4-hydroxybenzoate + H(+) -eq- CO(2) + phenol.
Catalysis of the reaction -  5-oxopent-3-ene-1,2,5-tricarboxylate -eq- 2-oxohept-3-enedioate + CO2.
Catalysis of the reaction -  trans-glutaconyl-CoA + H(+) -eq- but-2-enoyl-CoA + CO(2).
Catalysis of the reaction -  2,4-dihydroxy-hept-trans-2-ene-1,7-dioate -eq- pyruvate + succinic semialdehyde.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (3E)-4-(2-carboxyphenyl)-2-oxobut-3-enoate -eq- 2-carboxybenzaldehyde + pyruvate.
